<disp-quote>
 <p>
  <italic>“A sickly season,” the merchant said,</italic>
 </p>
 <p>
  <italic>“The town I left was filled with dead,</italic>
 </p>
 <p>
  <italic>and everywhere these queer red flies</italic>
 </p>
 <p>
  <italic>crawled upon the corpses’ eyes,</italic>
 </p>
 <p>
  <italic>eating them away.”</italic>
 </p>
